Flashcard(question: " Easter Egg", answer: "Non-malicious code that when invoked, displays an insider joke, hidden message, or secret feature"),
Flashcard(question: " Logic Bomb", answer: "Malicious code that has been inserted inside a program and will execute only when certain conditions have been met"),
Flashcard(question: " step 1 Malware removal", answer: "identify symptoms of a malware infection"),
Flashcard(question: " Step 2 Malware removal", answer: "Quarantine the infected systems"),
