Flashcard(question: " step 2 preventing malware", answer: "update and patch the OS and applications regularly"),
Flashcard(question: " step 3 preventing malware", answer: "educate and train end users on safe internet surfing practices"),
Flashcard(question: " Exploit Technique", answer: "Describes the specific method by which malware code infects a target host"),
